{"id": "ChIJe0NSUCG7woARr671f4nUpxI", "rating": 3.9, "userRatingCount": 74, "displayName": {"text": "COS", "languageCode": "fr"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJe0NSUCG7woARr671f4nUpxI/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tseE0zVmZXVWxyYkdReVFWZGxXRVF0U25ZdFdrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "Not a great experience at this location. Many employees walked by me and not a single one said hi or asked me if I wanted to start a fitting room despite carrying a bunch of options. I hate leaving bad reviews but this experience was bad enough for me to decide I’m never going back. Honestly if one person would’ve just said hi or even made eye contact with a smile that’s all it would’ve taken for me to have a decent experience. I feel like this was a great example of why people prefer shopping online.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Not a great experience at this location. Many employees walked by me and not a single one said hi or asked me if I wanted to start a fitting room despite carrying a bunch of options. I hate leaving bad reviews but this experience was bad enough for me to decide I’m never going back. Honestly if one person would’ve just said hi or even made eye contact with a smile that’s all it would’ve taken for me to have a decent experience. I feel like this was a great example of why people prefer shopping online.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kimberly Rose", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101956096512770120907/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoSjAVj7f_UceLU8R1DkOpOvNID03mRsSje9itzrdXi_A2Q91R=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-23T03:39:43.963396710Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tseE0zVmZXVWxyYkdReVFWZGxXRVF0U25ZdFdrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQ